We can look at how overvalued or undervalued a cryptocurrency is relative to its blockchain activity. Big values indicate an overbought asset, a small value means an asset is oversold.   This is a different approach to RSI, and is very useful tool if you a Value Investor. #TRON  https://t.co/n4C1iGCHj5

So we can derive a few statements about TRX from this dataset. There is no target value, it's a comparison tool.  -TRX is very undervalued?  -Either TRON as a product is overperforming relative to its market cap, or Ethereum is severely underperforming (and is maybe overvalued?)
